N

NEW_DATA_GPS - Variable in class carl.abr.threads.Main_thread
true: new data from the GPS is available after calling GPS_listener.get_location() in Main_thread.get_sensors_data().
NEW_DATA_IOIO - Variable in class carl.abr.threads.Main_thread
true: new data from the IOIO is available after calling get_IR_values() in Main_thread.get_ioio_data().
NEW_DECLI - Variable in class carl.abr.threads.Main_thread
true: used to get the earth declination only once in Main_thread.get_sensors_data().
NEW_FRAME - Variable in class carl.abr.IO.Camera_feedback
true: a new frame is available
false: the frame has already been accessed
NEW_FRAME - Variable in class carl.abr.threads.Main_thread
true: a new frame is available after calling Camera_feedback.get_data() in Main_thread.get_camera_data().
NEW_IMA - Variable in class carl.abr.threads.Main_thread
true: when camera starts, a new image (Main_thread.the_frame) will be created
false: the same image is then modified.
NEW_LOCATION - Variable in class carl.abr.IO.GPS_listener
true: a new location is available
false: the location has already been accessed and/or has not been updated yet.
